  "body": "Geth keeps crashing on a 4GB RAM x64 \nUbuntu box. Attached is the memory profile\n[mem.txt](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/files/505647/mem.txt)\n#### System information\n\nVersion: 1.4.13-stable\nProtocol Versions: [63 62]\nNetwork Id: 1\nGo Version: go1.5.1\nOS: linux\n#### Expected behaviour\n#### Actual behaviour\n\nOut of Memory. Geth crashes \n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n#### Backtrace\n\n```\ngoroutine 1206 [select]:\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p.(*protoRW).ReadMsg(0xc823dc7d50, 0x0, 0x7f2600000000, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0)\n        /home/ubuntu/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p/peer.go:357 +0x221\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth.(*ProtocolManager).handleMsg(0xc82037e0d0, 0xc8238575f0, 0x0, 0x0)\n        /home/ubuntu/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth/handler.go:314 +0x97\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth.(*ProtocolManager).handle(0xc82037e0d0, 0xc8238575f0, 0x0, 0x0)\n        /home/ubuntu/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth/handler.go:303 +0xb36\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth.NewProtocolManager.func1(0xc8e2846d00, 0x7f26755a0928, 0xc823dc7d50, 0x0, 0x0)\n        /home/ubuntu/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth/handler.go:138 +0x17b\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p.(*Peer).startProtocols.func1(0xc823dc7d50, 0xc8e2846d00)\n        /home/ubuntu/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p/peer.go:303 +0x8c\ncreated by github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p.(*Peer).startProtocols\n        /home/ubuntu/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/p2p/peer.go:312 +0x304\n```\n",
